      "chapter_title": "The Puppeteer's Shadow",
      "quest_type": "main",
      "required": true,
      "scale": "large",
      "quests": [
        {
          "quest_id": "Q2_1",
          "quest_title": "The Doctor's Trail",
          "steps": [
            {
              "step": 1,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "laboratory",
                "to": "village"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 2,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "village",
                "to": "outpost1"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 3,
              "action": "UNLOCK",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "key_item": "outpost_key_1",
                "target_place": "outpost1"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 4,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "outpost1",
                "to": "outpost2"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 5,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "outpost2",
                "to": "outpost3"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 6,
              "action": "TALK",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "target": "the_doctor",
                "place": "outpost3",
                "dialogue_content": [
                  {
                    "speaker": "player",
                    "line": "I know you're behind the chaos on this island. Viktor is your puppet, isn't he?"
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "the_doctor",
                    "line": "Puppet? Such a crude metaphor. Viktor is a variable I have optimized for control. He handles the brute force while I handle the science."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "player",
                    "line": "You're using the outbreak to test your theories. People are dying for your data."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "the_doctor",
                    "line": "Data requires a sample size, and tragedy is the most efficient catalyst for evolution. Viktor's security ensures my work isn't interrupted by... sentimentality."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "player",
                    "line": "I'm not leaving until I stop you. Where are you hiding your research?"
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "the_doctor",
                    "line": "My research is everywhere, and nowhere. But if you wish to see the source, you'll find the tools you need in this very room. Take the toolkit; it's the only thing I have no use for right now."
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 7,
              "action": "PICKUP",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "item": "toolkit_1",
                "place": "outpost3"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "quest_id": "Q2_2",
          "quest_title": "The Power of Truth",
          "steps": [
            {
              "step": 8,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "outpost3",
                "to": "outpost2"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 9,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "outpost2",
                "to": "outpost1"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 10,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "outpost1",
                "to": "village"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 11,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "village",
                "to": "powerstation"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 12,
              "action": "TALK",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "target": "george",
                "place": "powerstation",
                "dialogue_content": [
                  {
                    "speaker": "player",
                    "line": "George, The Doctor is pulling the strings. He's using Viktor to keep everyone distracted while he runs his experiments."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "george",
                    "line": "I suspected as much. The power grid fluctuations match his movement patterns. He needs the laboratory powered for his synthesis machine."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "player",
                    "line": "We need to cut his power. I have a toolkit, but I need to get a fuse to shut down the backup generator he's using."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "george",
                    "line": "The fuse is at the farm. Linda keeps it there. If you bring it back, I can isolate the grid. That will force him to the surface."
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 13,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "powerstation",
                "to": "village"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 14,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "village",
                "to": "farm"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 15,
              "action": "TALK",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "target": "linda",
                "place": "farm",
                "dialogue_content": [
                  {
                    "speaker": "player",
                    "line": "Linda, I need the fuse you're keeping here. The Doctor is using it to power his lab."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "linda",
                    "line": "I found it in the barn. Didn't know what it was, just knew it looked important. The Doctor's men were asking about it."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "player",
                    "line": "They were trying to keep his experiment running. I need to shut it down to expose him."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "linda",
                    "line": "Take it. Better it's in your hands than his. Just... be careful. The land doesn't like men who play god."
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 16,
              "action": "PICKUP",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "item": "food_supplies_1",
                "place": "farm"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 17,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "farm",
                "to": "village"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 18,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "village",
                "to": "powerstation"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 19,
              "action": "TURN_POWER_ON",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "fuse_item": "food_supplies_1",
                "place": "powerstation",
                "target_place": "laboratory"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "quest_id": "Q2_3",
          "quest_title": "The Confrontation",
          "steps": [
            {
              "step": 20,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "powerstation",
                "to": "village"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 21,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "village",
                "to": "laboratory"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 22,
              "action": "TALK",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "target": "sarah",
                "place": "laboratory",
                "dialogue_content": [
                  {
                    "speaker": "player",
                    "line": "Sarah, the power is cut. The Doctor's lab is dark. We need to get to the bottom of this."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "sarah",
                    "line": "Without power, his synthesis machine is dead. But he's still here. He's hiding in the lower levels of the outpost. We need to find the cure sample he stole."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "player",
                    "line": "I found the toolkit at his outpost. Maybe there's more evidence there. We need to go back and search."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "sarah",
                    "line": "Agreed. If he left anything behind, it will be in the cave where the key was. Let's move."
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 23,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "laboratory",
                "to": "village"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 24,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "village",
                "to": "cave"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 25,
              "action": "TALK",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "target": "sarah",
                "place": "cave",
                "dialogue_content": [
                  {
                    "speaker": "player",
                    "line": "Sarah, this is where the key was. Maybe the cure sample is here too."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "sarah",
                    "line": "Look over there. That crate was left open. It's empty, but the residue... it's the same as the cure sample. He moved it."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "player",
                    "line": "He must have taken it to the outpost. We need to go back and confront him before he leaves the island."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "sarah",
                    "line": "Agreed. If we can get the sample back, we can synthesize the cure and stop him for good."
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
